name: Wookiee_Choir_Master
content:
Wookiee Choir Master was a Male Wookiee who resided on Kashyyyk. He was upset that his bandmates were not in correct positions and were making a mockery of his performance. He wished that he could be a Jedi so that he could use The Force to move them into positions.
"Wookiee Choir Master" first appeared in the side-puzzle "Kachirho's Chorus" in the 2022 non-canonical video game LEGO Star Wars: The Skywalker Saga.
